messages.message:
Brian
I can't believe we weren't Facebook friends before!  I am doing great, how are you!?
Good of course. Nothing too exciting in boring, old Tucson. How's Flagstaff treating you? When are NAU's finals? Are they the same week as ours?

Brian
Flagstaff is nice, I have been having a lot of parties.  I think finals are the same week as ASU.  Like the second week of May?
